    "en": {
      "title": "US Ambassador meets President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); President Gotabaya Rajapaksa met with the USA Ambassador in Sri Lanka Julie J. Ching today (30) and thanked the US for the valuable support shown during these difficult times.",
        "Further, the Ambassador assured the Government of the USA\u2019s continuous support in stabilizing the economy with the recent developments with the International Monetary Fund (IMF).",
        "US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Chung told President Gotabaya Rajapaksa that the US will support Sri Lanka in finding a solution to the economic crisis.",
        "A high-level diplomatic delegation from the United States stated that the US supports the strengthening of the relationship with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "US President Joe Biden has also taken steps to provide humanitarian assistance on several occasions."
      ],
